    <h3 class="closing-title heading-font">
      Want to Talk About Projects or Collaboration?<span class="mark_green"
        >_</span
      >
    </h3>
    <p>
      Whether you have an exciting project in mind or you're looking for a
      collaborative opportunity, I'm here to explore the possibilities with you.
      Reach out, and let's start a conversation that could lead to something
      extraordinary. Together, we can turn ideas into reality and make a
      meaningful impact in the digital realm. Get in touch today and let's
      create something amazing together.
    </p>
    <div class="contact-icons-container">
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/zakyirwansyahandhika/"
        target="_blank">
        <i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i>
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/azzaky9"
